1
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:38,920
Boss, these are the things he brought.

2
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,180
I'll leave them to you.

3
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:03,160
We haven't seen each other for so many years,

4
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:05,420
and this is the greeting gift you give me?

5
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:11,120
If I had known earlier that you were Brother Hei,

6
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:13,320
I wouldn't have gone to so much trouble.

7
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,170
That's true.

8
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,530
In the eyes of Officer Shao,

9
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:18,760
people like us

10
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,440
are at your beck and

11
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,520
call.

12
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,640
You guys go out first.

13
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,440
I'm going to catch up

14
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,259
with my old friend.

15
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:36,800
Boss.

16
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,840
You know,

17
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,100
after all these years,

18
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,940
you haven't changed a bit.

19
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,400
You always expect to say nothing

20
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:34,340
and have people do things for you.

21
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:37,460
Extra green onions, no cilantro, right?

22
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,570
I didn't expect you to still be running this shop.

23
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:04,520
This shop,

24
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,120
Lao Bai gave it to me.

25
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,080
Back then,

26
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,410
he was always making empty promises to me.

27
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,000
He said that in the future...

28
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,000
After I help you deal with Sang Rong,

29
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,280
you'll run this shop with me.

30
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,370
We'll make it a national chain,

31
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,260
and eventually go public.

32
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,280
As the lady boss,

33
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:29,720
wouldn't I just be lying back and counting money then?

34
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,720
You have to try these beef meatballs later.

35
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:36,050
These have been beaten over 10,000 times.

36
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:39,440
Lao Bai used to say,

37
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,200
these beef meatballs

38
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,730
must be beaten 10,000 times

39
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,840
to be the chewiest

40
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,090
and most delicious.

41
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,250
He didn't have time before,

42
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,620
so he'd beat them 3,000 times at most.

43
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,960
You should try them later

44
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:56,490
and see if the taste is really that different.

45
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,600
I'm sorry.

46
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:04,180
You already said that four years ago.

47
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,800
What's the point?

48
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:11,520
You promised to find out

49
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,920
who betrayed Lao Bai.

50
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:18,079
It's been so many years.

51
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,850
Where is the answer?

52
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,840
Although I haven't been a cop for a long time,

53
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,120
I've actually been

54
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,170
investigating this in secret.

55
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,720
Including Sang Rong's side

56
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,850
and our department.

57
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,840
It doesn't really matter

58
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,760
who it is.

59
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,480
You said Lao Bai was your informant,

60
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:50,520
and only you and I in the whole world know his identity.

61
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,600
As for Lao Bai,

62
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:54,320
I know him best.

63
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,320
He acts cautiously

64
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,250
and flawlessly.

65
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:00,320
So the problem couldn't have come from him.

66
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:05,520
Either you accidentally leaked the information,

67
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:12,320
or you have a mole over there.

68
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,320
But if there's a mole,

69
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,840
how did he know about this?

70
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:21,960
You can't get away

71
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,880
from Lao Bai's death.

72
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,760
Have you been sleeping well lately?

73
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,980
I've been dreaming about Lao Bai lately.

74
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,400
He often asks me in my dreams,

75
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,680
how are you doing?

76
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:42,040
As you can see,

77
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,860
I'm doing pretty well.

78
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,560
Now I can even

79
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:50,740
eat these beef meatballs pounded 10,000 times.

80
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,000
And that's all thanks to you.

81
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,890
If you hadn't taken down Sang Rong,

82
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,640
I wouldn't necessarily

83
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,370
have had this chance in my life.

84
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,040
Are you enjoying the food,

85
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,840
Hei?

86
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,540
Isn't that because you're incompetent?

87
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,860
Just because you can't handle it,

88
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:27,120
doesn't mean Lao Bai's case can just be brushed aside.

89
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,000
You can let it go,

90
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,960
but I can't.

91
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,920
I will never get over it in my life.

92
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:03,360
Much better.

93
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,800
Speak.

94
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,760
You made such a big fuss

95
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,680
just to see me.

96
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,160
What is it?

97
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,400
Wang Yu.

98
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,530
Why are you looking for her?

99
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,920
My daughter was kidnapped.

100
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,480
The kidnapper forced me to find you

101
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,360
and say this name.

102
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,120
He said as long as I say it,

103
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,380
you would understand.

104
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:31,920
Okay.

105
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:34,220
I can tell you where she is.

106
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,720
But

107
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,659
you have to do something for me first.

108
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,920
He gave me a time limit.

109
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,440
If I exceed this time frame,

110
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,100
my daughter will be in danger.

111
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,320
That's your problem.

112
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,200
Okay.

113
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:52,760
Tell me.

114
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,200
A friend of mine

115
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,320
lost three million in a casino.

116
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,890
I will give you one million in capital.

117
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:03,440
You help me win back that three million.

118
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,560
Why do you think I can win it back for you?

119
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:11,640
Weren't you an undercover in that gambling syndicate before?

120
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:14,300
You know their techniques and tricks very well.

121
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,880
And it seems

122
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,760
the guy running the place

123
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:21,000
is an old acquaintance of yours.

124
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,680
Don't you want to see him?

125
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,600
It's broken.

126
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,400
I'm fine, Boss.

127
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,840
Who did this?

128
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,420
What happened?

129
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:46,520
Well...

130
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,880
He got someone's sister pregnant.

131
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,330
Don't you think he deserved a beating?

132
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,440
As for me,

133
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,040
unlike some people,

134
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:07,840
I won't let my brothers get bullied.

135
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,890
I know what you want to play.

136
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,520
Okay.

137
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,620
I'll give you a chance.

138
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,760
You go home first.

139
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:43,700
I'll have someone send the capital to you later.

140
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:44,920
Also,

141
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,210
that stab just now counts as interest.

142
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,640
You go with him and win the money back,

143
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:52,850
and our grudge will be written off.

144
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,780
If you can't win it back...

145
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,160
Brother Hei.

146
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,400
I have to go back now

147
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,600
to see my girlfriend.

148
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,000
My silly brother,

149
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:14,370
do you really think your girlfriend is pregnant?

150
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,240
You have

151
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,720
to take this off.

152
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:49,570
You might need to take off this underwear too.

153
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,810
Maybe I should get someone to help.

154
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,960
Thank you.

155
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,600
It's all taken care of.

156
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,860
It's nothing serious.

157
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,120
I'm cooking right now.

158
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,720
Stay for a meal before you go.

159
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:34,580
No, thanks.

160
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,080
I won't disturb you anymore.

161
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,920
Besides, I ordered takeout.

162
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,340
It should be here soon.

163
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,920
I'll get going then.

164
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,000
By the way,

165
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:49,060
get your injuries looked at as soon as possible.

166
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,140
Can you eat thick noodles?

167
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:16,920
Okay.

168
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:30,440
I'll go downstairs to buy something to drink.

169
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,680
What's wrong?

170
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:55,730
Nothing.

171
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:04,480
I had minor surgery.

172
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:16,240
Don't drink if you're injured.

173
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:25,440
Didn't you just get injured too?

174
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,520
Just now,

175
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,250
when I was treating your wound.

176
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,440
I saw that

177
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,080
on your back,

178
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,410
there are...

179
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,220
there are a lot.

180
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,640
It's all in the past.

181
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,010
Here is one million.

182
00:14:22,640 --> 00:14:23,570
I have something

183
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,650
to talk to her about in private.

184
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:32,180
Just say what you have to say here.

185
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,210
She can hear you.

186
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,460
That's between her and me.

187
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:37,060
It's not for your ears.

188
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:40,160
What if I insist on listening?
